Title	" Water and stiff oil phase separation "
Date    03/02/23
Comment	" 75:25 mixture of water and oil to see them phase separate. The cross interaction parameter
          is very large to ensure rapid separation.
          Oil is stiff, quite closely space, and fairly long
           "


